        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: '1', 2: 'Hassen', 3: 'What follows is classified info.', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 24,
        "ActionId": 23,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Hassen', 3: 'During Operation Acadia, we recovered a massive corpus of data through Gestalt for the operation of Babylonia and the rebuilding of human civilization.', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 25,
        "ActionId": 24,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Hassen', 3: 'There were some data that were submitted in our logs, but cannot be found inside the database.', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 26,
        "ActionId": 25,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Hassen', 3: 'And with everything that Babylonia has been through since its conception, tracing where the files have gone has become immensely difficult.', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 27,
        "ActionId": 26,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Hassen', 3: 'But enough about the past. The top priority right now is to retrieve the lost files.', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 28,
        "ActionId": 27,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Hassen', 3: 'There are some data blocks that we didn\\'t have the time to go through back then. I\\'ve attached their locations to this message. Please have a look.', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 29,
        "ActionId": 28,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Murray', 3: 'President Hassen, I\\'m not a direct subordinate of yours right now... Is it really appropriate to give me this kind of mission?', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 30,
        "ActionId": 29,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Hassen', 3: 'You\\'d know best.', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 31,
        "ActionId": 30,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Hassen', 3: 'Working under Nikola has its advantages, which is why you joined him on the surface. No?', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 32,
        "ActionId": 31,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 204,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: '1', 2: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 33,
        "ActionId": 32,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Murray', 3: 'Just trying to move things in a better direction. It\\'s what everyone would have done.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 34,
        "ActionId": 33,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Hassen', 3: 'Which is why I know you\\'d accept my mission.', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 35,
        "ActionId": 34,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Murray', 3: '...What can I say? You see right through me, President Hassen. But the issue remains—I don\\'t think I should learn of the info within these files.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 36,
        "ActionId": 35,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Murray', 3: 'After all, I quite value my life.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 37,
        "ActionId": 36,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Hassen', 3: 'I\\'ll tell you the end game... These files are the embers that can end this war.', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 38,
        "ActionId": 37,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Hassen', 3: 'Everything we\\'ve done has been to end the war, and these files can forward this objective immensely.', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 39,
        "ActionId": 38,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Hassen', 3: 'I don\\'t think I have to remind you of the confidentiality level of these files.', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 40,
        "ActionId": 39,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 204,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 41,
        "ActionId": 40,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Murray', 3: 'Pardon me, but why not directly extract the files yourself? But rather, have me retrieve them first, then relay them to you?', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 42,
        "ActionId": 41,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Hassen', 3: 'There are quite a few reasons, but none that should concern you.', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 43,
        "ActionId": 42,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Murray', 3: '...President Hassen, you are just like Commander Nikola sometimes.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 44,
        "ActionId": 43,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Hassen', 3: 'I get that a lot.', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 45,
        "ActionId": 44,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Hassen', 3: 'Enough with the chit-chat. Time\\'s ticking.', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 46,
        "ActionId": 45,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Hassen', 3: 'Once I express interest in these files, Nikola will certainly react immediately.', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 47,
        "ActionId": 46,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Hassen', 3: 'If you think I\\'m like him, then you must also know what makes us different. Especially on our views about certain things.', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 48,
        "ActionId": 47,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Hassen', 3: 'For this tiny sliver of hope, are you willing to take the risk?', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 49,
        "ActionId": 48,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Murray', 3: '...Well, I don\\'t think I have a choice.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 50,
        "ActionId": 49,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Hassen', 3: 'In that case, good luck.', 4: '2'}"
    },
